---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Playground | Toby on Fitness Tech"
  description="IronVane-Episoden, Fitness-Spiele und Trainings-Apps — alles an einem Ort."
>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-neutral-950 text-white py-12 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          🎮 Spielplatz
        </h1>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 text-lg">
          IronVane-Episoden, Fitness-Spiele und Trainings-Apps — alles an einem Ort.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* ── IRONVANE / CROSSFIRE ── */}
      <div class="mb-14">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
          <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500">⚔️ IronVane</h2>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@IronVaneStory" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sm text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors flex items-center gap-1">
            YouTube-Kanal →
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8">
          <article class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="p-5 pb-3">
              <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500">Episode 1</span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-1">IronVane — EP1</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="px-5 pb-5 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">YouTube</p>
                <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden w-full aspect-video bg-neutral-800">
                  <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/L9VfUQxVRe0" class="w-full h-full" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Rumble</p>
                <div id="rumble_v7653si_de" class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden w-full aspect-video bg-neutral-800"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="p-5 pb-3">
              <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500">Episode 2</span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-1">IronVane — EP2</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="px-5 pb-5 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">YouTube</p>
                <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden w-full aspect-video bg-neutral-800">
                  <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/DT-co7MkzaY" class="w-full h-full" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Rumble</p>
                <div id="rumble_v766b6u_de" class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden w-full aspect-video bg-neutral-800"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="p-5 pb-3">
              <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500">Crossfire — Episode 3</span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-1">Die Entführten</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="px-5 pb-5 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">YouTube</p>
                <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden w-full aspect-video bg-neutral-800">
                  <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/lVGU2dFNTU4" class="w-full h-full" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Rumble</p>
                <div id="rumble_v768cyw_de" class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden w-full aspect-video bg-neutral-800"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500 mb-4">🕹️ Spiele</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-10">
        <article class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 p-6 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">MMA RPG</h3>
            <span class="text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-900/40 border border-green-500/40 text-green-300">🟢 Live</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4">Ein rundenbasiertes MMA-Kampf-RPG. Erstelle deinen Kämpfer, meistere Kombos und arbeite dich in den Rängen nach oben.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Kampf</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">RPG</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Strategie</span>
          </div>
          <a href="https://tobyonfitnesstech.com/mma-rpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-3 rounded-xl bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 transition-colors font-semibold">
            ▶ Jetzt spielen
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 p-6 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Gridbound Realms</h3>
            <span class="text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-900/40 border border-green-500/40 text-green-300">🟢 Live</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4">Ein taktisches Strategiespiel auf Rasterbasis. Kommandiere deine Einheiten und erobere das Reich.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Strategie</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Taktik</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Raster</span>
          </div>
          <a href="https://tobyonfitnesstech.com/gridbound-realms" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-3 rounded-xl bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 transition-colors font-semibold">
            ▶ Jetzt spielen
          </a>
        </article>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500 mb-4">📱 Apps</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <article class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 p-6 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">BJJ Buddy</h3>
            <span class="text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-900/40 border border-green-500/40 text-green-300">🟢 Live</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4">Verfolge dein BJJ-Training, protokolliere Runden, beobachte deinen Fortschritt und bring dein Grappling aufs nächste Level.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">BJJ</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Trainingslog</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Fortschritt</span>
          </div>
          <a href="https://tobyonfitnesstech.com/bjj-buddy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-3 rounded-xl bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-500 transition-colors font-semibold">
            🥋 App öffnen
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 p-6 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">NutriTrack</h3>
            <span class="text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-900/40 border border-green-500/40 text-green-300">🟢 Live</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4">Kostenloses Ernährungstracking. Protokolliere Mahlzeiten, erreiche deine Makros und unterstütze dein Training gezielt.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Ernährung</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Makros</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Mahlzeitenprotokoll</span>
          </div>
          <a href="https://nutritrack.tobyonfitnesstech.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-3 rounded-xl bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-500 transition-colors font-semibold">
            🥗 App öffnen
          </a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<script is:inline>
  (function(r,u,m,b,l,e){r._Rumble=b,r[b]||(r[b]=function(){(r[b]._=r[b]._||[]).push(arguments);if(r[b]._.length==1){l=u.createElement(m),e=u.getElementsByTagName(m)[0],l.async=1,l.src="https://rumble.com/embedJS/u4p7v1q/?url="+encodeURIComponent(location.href)+"&args="+encodeURIComponent(JSON.stringify([].slice.apply(arguments))),e.parentNode.insertBefore(l,e)}})})(window, document, "script", "Rumble");
  Rumble("play", {"video":"v7653si","div":"rumble_v7653si_de"});
  Rumble("play", {"video":"v766b6u","div":"rumble_v766b6u_de"});
  Rumble("play", {"video":"v768cyw","div":"rumble_v768cyw_de"});
